To ensure our app supports multiple languages, all user-facing strings **must be wrapped using Lingui's i18n tools**.

Use either:

```tsx
import { Trans } from '@lingui/react';

<Trans id="Welcome to Zync" />
```

or:

```tsx
import { useLingui } from '@lingui/react';

const { t } = useLingui();
t`Welcome to Zync`;
```

